name: Delphine Stamp
description:
Send your mail in style with this classic calligraphy style stamp. Perfect for your everyday paper lovelies, thank you notes or for addressing your wedding invitation envelopes. Need a thoughtful gift? Great for house-warming, weddings, birthdays and holidays!

This is a self-inking stamp with black ink, no need to buy an ink pad! 
The maximum printable area for this stamp is 2.25 x 1 inches.

Yours Truly Ordering Process:
1. Place your order and include the name and address you would like on your stamp under 'note to seller'.
2. Yours Truly will send you a proof via email within 2 business days.
3. Upon proof approval, your stamp will be produced and shipped within 7-10 business days.

Have a question? Email us at bilodeau.melissa@gmail.com.
